summary: Completed comprehensive testing of Hypd Games mobile-first instant gaming website. Core functionality working well with TikTok-style feed, game playing, and admin features. Found minor UI overlay issues affecting some interactions.

ui_bugs.issue: Emergent badge overlay intercepting pointer events preventing Profile tab clicks
Dialog overlay intercepting pointer events when modals are open, preventing seed games button clicks

passed_tests: Game Feed loads with vertical snap scroll
Play Now button navigation to game player
HTML5 games load and play correctly in fullscreen iframe
Back button navigation returns to feed
Explore page with search and category filtering
Admin dashboard loads and displays games
Game management buttons (edit, visibility, delete) present
Sample games seeded successfully (4 games: Neon Blocks, Space Dodge, Color Match, Cyber Runner)
Bottom navigation between tabs (Feed, Explore, PRO, Profile)
action_item_for_main_agent: Fix UI overlay issues: 1) Emergent badge z-index preventing Profile tab clicks, 2) Modal dialog overlays preventing interactions with background buttons. Consider adjusting z-index values or pointer-events CSS properties.
